main event: A witness reported observing a satellite zigzagging and moving up and down while traveling on January 5, 1962.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 1 minute,The satellite was visible at an elevation of 35 degrees above the horizon,The object was identified as a possible satellite observation,The object was noted to have no identifying markings,The satellite was tracked as it moved from west to east.
witness description: the witness was traveling and saw the satellite
